## What "done" looks like for December 2026

**The product is ready if:**
- All 9 pillars (1-9) feel polished, not rushed
- Onboarding works in under 60 seconds
- Mobile (PWA) works smoothly on iPhone and Android
- Stripe charges and refunds work flawlessly
- All paid pilot feedback has been incorporated
- Cy responds reliably with the load redistribution capability
- No critical bugs reported by paid pilot users in November

**The audience is ready if:**
- 2,500+ engaged newsletter subscribers
- 8+ months of consistent Sunday newsletter cadence
- 20+ podcast episodes published
- 25+ essays on thehousewebuilt.family
- At least 5 substantive case studies / testimonials from beta

**The team is ready if:**
- Remi has capacity to support 50-100 incoming families in December
- Kendra has sustained sustainable writing pace for 8 months
- Sunday check-in has been consistent throughout
- Neither of us has burned out
- Marriage is stronger, not weaker, after the build

